ap is in reasonable agreement with expectations from other\nstudies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2007 09:05:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2007 15:26:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
