stablish the hydrodynamic limit for a ZRP with discontinuous speed-parameter\ngoverned by an entropy solution to our PDE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2007 11:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-10-02"}
